  "system": {
    "description": {
      "value": "<p>You have access to an iconic sword. <br />Either one of ancient legend or one of recent fame. <br />This sword is bound to it, and upon its death, it is banished back to the Mist Village to inform its Mizukage of the wielders Demise. <br />This weapon is a +2 Odachi, that uses the highest ability score of the wielder as its ability score required to wield, and calculate attack and damage rolls, it also has one Jutsu of C-Rank or Lower Sealed into it. <br />This jutsu can be cast from the sword as a Bonus action, regardless of its normal casting time, and costs one of its seven charges.</p>",
